===Alternative forms===
Note that the standard [[Kangxi]] form is written with [[刀]] on top. The current form in traditional and simplified Chinese script is however written with [[⺈]] on top. In Korean, the Kangxi form with [[刀]] on top is retained. A compatibility ideograph (U+2F80F) exists for the Kangxi character with [[刀]] on top.

===Usage notes===
In Japanese, the [[unorthodox]] character ([[俗字]]) of 兔, [[兎]] is used instead. 

